<p>Cheers! The ending did give me some grief - I did consider a fight sequence between the Bagman and the MTF, but it seemed tacked-on and out of true with the rest of the Tale, which as mentioned in the Author's Notes isn't exactly high-octane. A trade rather than a fight also seemed more inkeeping with the themes of the piece. If I were to go back and revisit the piece I would look at expanding 'Castle' and further developing what we see of the Foundation.</p>

